# Never Modify Submodule Code Directly

external/ contains all submodules.  Submodule code should never be modified directly. To extend or customize submodule functionality, always use one of the following approaches:

- Wrapper scripts
- Extension apps
- Configuration overrides

This ensures that submodules remain upgradable and maintainable, and prevents merge conflicts or loss of custom changes when updating the submodule.
